    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_453_23",
    "text": "I watched as m itle brother was caugh in the act. He was siting in the corer of the living room, 36 in one hand and my father's hymnbook（赞美诗集）in the other.",
