  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_453_24",
    "text": "As my father walked into the room, my brother cowered slightly（轻微地畏缩）.He sensed that he had done something 37 . I could see that he had 38 my father's new hymnal and scribbled （乱 涂）in it. Now he was waiting for his punishment. h",
